# ===========================================
# Production Security Checklist
# ===========================================

# Before going to production, ensure:
# ✅ JWT_SECRET is random and at least 32 characters
# ✅ DB_PASS is strong and unique
# ✅ CORS_ORIGINS is restrictive (not "*")
# ✅ APP_ENV is set to "production"
# ✅ APP_DEBUG is set to "false"
# ✅ SECURITY_REQUIRE_HTTPS is "true"
# ✅ All database credentials are environment variables
# ✅ SSL certificate is installed and configured
# ✅ Regular backups are scheduled
# ✅ Error logging is monitored
# ✅ Rate limiting is tested
# ✅ Security headers are verified
